{"tid":1760484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國防部重申止暴制亂　稱駐港部隊隨時聽從指揮","createTime":"2019-11-28T08:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T11:30:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":138,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":135,"replies":[{"pid":"3e878a56bd493cff2e156c855819e21571f95257","tid":1760484,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"中國國防部周四（28日）舉行記者會時，記者就香港情況提問，國防部新聞發言人任國強回應，解放軍駐港部隊隨時聽從黨中央、中央軍委的指揮。<br />\n<br />\n針對軍隊在香港止暴制亂是否會採取措施，任國強表示，關於香港局勢，國家主席習近平發表了重要講話，發出中央政府對香港局勢止暴制亂工作的最強音，為穩定香港局勢指明方向和路徑。<br />\n<br />\n任國強稱，解放軍駐港部隊隨時聽從黨中央、中央軍委的指揮，有決心、有信心、有能力履行好基本法和駐軍法賦予的職責使命，堅決維護國家主權、安全和發展利益，堅決維護香港長期穩定、繁榮發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191128/bkn-20191128163243039-1128_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191128%2Fbkn-20191128163243039-1128_00952_001.html&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a3bd754d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191128/bkn-20191128163243039-1128_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"adfaec561454844f4a2e263589708f06eb0e0ad4","tid":1760484,"uid":293677,"like":143,"dislike":1,"score":142,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfLXv00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfLXv00.png&h=d7c99e8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9780d3afc525bb2f8f323a00a02147ab2b8d5deb","tid":1760484,"uid":59328,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"出啦好悶呀！"},{"pid":"c6296317a1c358157d5110edc99ee3548f52d477","tid":1760484,"uid":64313,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"止暴制亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係popo可以寫定遺書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a367b76cd783a94120654b5884cd51998d79f344","tid":1760484,"uid":73340,"like":3