發言人任國強回應，解放軍駐港部隊隨時聽從黨中央、中央軍委的指揮。<br />\n<br />\n針對軍隊在香港止暴制亂是否會採取措施，任國強表示，關於香港局勢，國家主席習近平發表了重要講話，發出中央政府對香港局勢止暴制亂工作的最強音，為穩定香港局勢指明方向和路徑。<br />\n<br />\n任國強稱，解放軍駐港部隊隨時聽從黨中央、中央軍委的指揮，有決心、有信心、有能力履行好基本法和駐軍法賦予的職責使命，堅決維護國家主權、安全和發展利益，堅決維護香港長期穩定、繁榮發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191128/bkn-20191128163243039-1128_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191128%2Fbkn-20191128163243039-1128_00952_001.html&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a3bd754d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191128/bkn-20191128163243039-1128_00952_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:28:36.000Z","msg":"會唔會係打9 popo<br />\n換取法案唔制裁中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外交部召見美大使：法案不得制裁中共官員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1760449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1760449</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"960d4149023206093a36c6e0bef31cab87d4c4a8","tid":1760484,"uid":73333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a485ba17580d982589a3fe0c8ceae6079100430","tid":1760484,"uid":109249,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgGvQ4K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgGvQ4K.png&h=533273f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"台灣：屌你咪打尖啦， 我等左咁多年。你先等幾個月收下皮先"},{"pid":"1749cbe91f21316a51ef5b58061335e02242262f","tid":1760484,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"5b2e378b1aa829f73348eac1e9ab42180f23a3b6","tid":1760484,"uid":230442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6281b4f603f8875a348d330e3054e20d6a05f266","tid":1760484,"uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www